Dialogs.Dialog: 高嶺
Did you have your first dream of the year? I had a dream about a golden rabbit.
Mmm~. I hope it was a good dream.
Fufu. Hey, if you could choose it yourself, what would you like to dream of?
One Fuji, two eagles, three eggplants!
Of course, it would be ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s dream!
I've never seen it... It would be nice if we could see it together, right?... I'm kidding.
...Geez. Then next will, can I visit you in your dreams?
Maybe not only in dreams... Hmm, it's nothing.
高嶺
Ha~a... It's cold, isn't it?
Right! But, isn't this a good thing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Hmm. But... it gets cold when we're together...right?
I see, it's the same
Warm wach other?
Really? Then... can I go a little closer? Then... hold my hands... tight.
Yes, please. I want you to warm me up... I'm kidding...
高嶺
It's a nice scent...
This smells is... plum blossom. It feels like spring is just around the corner.
Hmm. I wonder from where the scent comes from... Well then, shall we find it next time?
Alright, let's do it!
I found Manaka's flower
Oh...Ohー!... Ah, didn't you say it too loud? It's embarrassing...
Then, you're my sun... I'm kidding... Geez, don't make me say that anymore.
高嶺
Ah, Sakura petals...
It's beautiful, but it's a pity that it's scattered around.
Hmm. I want to see it all the time.
No! ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s line of sight is me!
I wish time stopped like this... I'm kidding?
! Hmm. Um... Geez, don't say that. Don't look this way?
Fufu, hmm. I think I can spend eternity with you... Hmm, I want to spend it with you.
I hope you think so too.
高嶺
...Ah~, I'm sorry! I've been very sleepy lately... I don't have lack off sleep though...
You're cute like that!
I'll show you what that is!
I don't believe it, even if it's fun... I don't believe it.
Do you make calls or send mails late every night?
That way, I'm happy to be connected to you until I fall asleep.
I yearn for it a little.
高嶺
Ah~... did you see? It's beautiful.
Ah, it's a rose. This season is for roses.
That's right. The whole month of May is for roses.
Flowers are said to be as beautiful as the care you give them, so the people took good care of them.
Like your parents did
They lose to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
Papa and Mama are gardeners? Or... is it you? Fufu~▼
That again... If you look at me with those eyes, I'll believe you, right? Geez...
高嶺
Were past half the year, right? Next week, it's already July...
That's right, it's going really quick.
Right. Looking back... all I can see is you.
Like a year's end greeting
This year is about us!
Hmm. I'm sure it will be at the end of this year, and the next. Even beyond that? Fufu!
We dyed it with our colors! I'm kidding.... Someday, we'll paint it together, right?
高嶺
It's still a long time for winter vacation, isn't it?
Hmm? It's kind of unusual for you to say that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Fufu, I don't hate school.
However. the summer vacation is over. I wonder what can we do during winter vacation.
I can't wait until winter!
Alright, I'll make a plan!
...Hmm, maybe that's right? Something sharp?
...Fufu, but what will you do? That's a way of saying "Let me do it!... Fufufu!
Starting now? ...Hmm, winter vacation is short.
I think if we start right now, we can probably do a lot of things. Shall we think together?
高嶺
When changing winter clothes to summer clothes, it seems that I forgot to put insect repellent...
You mean... something was eaten by worms?
Hmm, it was Papa's favorite sweater. Mama hand-knitted it...
Your mom was surprised too
When thinking about your dad
Yes, but she was enthusiastic about knitting a new one. Thank you for worrying.
I wonder if it's something men can share with each other.
Someday, I'm sure I'll get the chance to speak with Papa and tell him about it, right?
高嶺
Fu~u. It's a little hot, isn't it?
Even though it's October.
I think it was a failure for the summer clothes.
Actually, it's not that!
I'll fan you, come closer
Is that so? Hmm, then I lost my time... I'm kidding♪
Yes▼... But if I get too close, it will be hotter rather than cool, right?
高嶺
This is suddenly a problem. October is also called "Kannasuki".
Oops, Is is a quiz? Bring it on!
Month called "Kannazuki"?
...Check it with the phone?
It's October, I said it...
Yes, go ahead▼ It's important to find out what you don't understand with away.
...Fufu~, as expected. But next time I won't lose, okay?
高嶺
I woke up early this morning, so I went to hit the wall...
Oh, I'll do my best in the mornings too.
Fufu, yeah. You know, the water puddles were frozen. It must be cold, right?
I've to find ice!
Did you like that?
Is there any place left this time? Let's do it, let's make things crunchy with ice♪
...How do you know? Geez... I don't like it... I'm lying, though.
高嶺
Do you think it is true that the warbler sounds differently depending on the place and age?
I don't think I've heard of such thing...
Is there an accent in that area, or is there a senior warbler teaching how to sing?
If so, isn't it cute?
Let's check it!
I think you're better at it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Fufu, right? All over Japan, together... I hope we can do it someday▼
That's what I'm talking about... Shall we go? C'mon, let's hurry, right?
高嶺
In the evening right? I saw the news about a huge rabbit.
How big is it?
Um... A man picked it up, and it reached the tip of his foot to his knee, right?
And its weight is... about half of mine?
Ah, it was so fluffy!
I should hug you!
Fufufu, right?
Hey, can we go to the zoo next time? I want to go to the petting corner▼
Eh~! Um... right here...?... Geez, no!
高嶺
Ah, a cat.
Where?
Look, over there. Two of them are snuggling up and grooming. It's so cute...
I want to pet them
I wont lose to them!
Hmm, if you get in the way, you'll be kicked by a horse. Well, maybe not a horse, but a cat, right? Fufufu!
Geez, I'm not trying to compete .... But I agree. More tight ... right?
高嶺
The dog I saw earlier...
Oh, it was cute! With its round eyes, swinging its tail! I wanted to hug it!
Umm... I mean... right?
Please don't worry.
But, if you don't take care of me, I might feel a little lonely... I'm kidding.
...As a punishmen, how about huging me? I have a lot of things to do today.
高嶺
The other day, right? I was invited by the basketball club advisor to join.
Eh!... You didn't accept, right?
...How knows, right?
I'll go with you!
You must be in tennis club!
Fufu~, transfering together? It's okay, I won't go. Let's do our best in the tennis club, right?
...Hey, can you say something more? Then I'll think about it... I'm kidding.
Manaka will never leave you▼ Fufu!
高嶺
Have you seen Suzuki- sensei's mobile phone?
Mobile phone? No, but why?
The standby screen is the picture of a child. It looks like he takes a lot of photos.
It seems he goes "dere"!
I'll do the same, I'm sure...
Hmm, I guess its really cute. Would you like me to ask him to show it next time? Fufu!
Is that going to happen?
Before that, can you fill you phone with my photos? I'm kidding!
高嶺
Rumor has it that the length of the uniform skirt will be longer, but... is it true?
Seriously!?
...Hmm? Is that bad?
Umm... Not much?
Ah, it matches you ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
Really?... Geez, your eyes are waving. Pervert.
...Fufu! "I said something good", your face is like that.
From cute to unquestioned▼ I'm kidding.
高嶺
I have a friend who calls his father by his name... Is that natural?
Hmm, I wonder about it. It seems it's becoming a common thing.
That's right... If I did that, I might be disowned.
Why don't you try it here?
If it happens, come with me!
Eh~, uh... I won't do it! Geez, of you tell me that, I won't do it.
..."It's a joke", I don't need to hear that... Geez.
高嶺
Is my wording strange?
Hmmー, is that so?
I was told that it's not modern... How modern is it?
Something like "srly"?
I want you to stay that way!
Did you hear that before? “Serious” is "Really”, isn't it?... Srly? Hmm...
...Yes, I understand▼ But, I'm curious...
Hey, can you tell me about it next time? When studying together, right~?
高嶺
There's a boy who sing in a band, right? I was asked to play the keyboard...
Mmm~, what kind of band?
A rock band. But I wonder if it's okay.
You're so intense ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
You don't need to say that!
Geez, what are you imagining? It's nothing that violent!
...But, would you like to see me too?
I see... I don't know much about rock. If you have a recommended rock band, let me know.
高嶺
The other day, I played a difficult piano piece for the first time in a long time.
Oh, how was it?
It was alright. I have to practice more at home.
I want to hear it too!
I also like that place
... No. Because I would say... "Don't look at me like that".
So I wish I could play more, right?
In that place... I absolutely love you...
高嶺
Last night, I watched Cinderella after a long time.
Anime? On DVD?
Yes, that's right. It was wonderful.
I also want to see it...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you're a little
Then, shall we watch it together in my room next time? Fufu~, I'm looking forward to it.
Childing... maybe. But I like it more now, because I met a real prince▼
高嶺
I wonder if something good will come out of the cleaning goods...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I think you're addicted to that.
Geez... But, do you think so?
It's a prospect, I think
I think it's cute
You know me better than myself, right?... Fufu, it's tickling.
That's not an answer... Why do you always say that? Geez...
高嶺
I've always thought that my sleep posture isn't bad, right?
Hmm? Something happened?
Yeah, I fell out of bed last night. It's been a while since I was so surprised... so I laughed.
Did you fall head-first?
I wanted to see it!
Fufu~, yes, it used to happen when I was little. Why was I moving so much?
Then, next time... Can't you ask?... Idiot.
高嶺
Hey, I have a question.
Yes, go ahead!
Fufu~! You know? I wonder what kind of people your friends are like.
Are you interested in them?
No, I won't introduce you!
It's no good then. Your girlfriend wants to know everything about you. I'm kidding.
Geez, that's not the case... Hey, did you get jealous? So cute▼
高嶺
Is blogging interesting?
Some people find it interesting. Are you thinking about doing it?
Hmm... I haven't decided yet. You know, there are many people doing it.
Shall we do a love diary?
Do something crazy!
Eh~... is there something like that?... Then, should we stop? I want to keep them in secret... I'm kidding.
...I can't be more crazy than you. Don't do anything weird. Boo! Fufu!
高嶺
I sometimes see it...
Hmm? What?
How is the person who has two mobile phones using them? How would you use it?
Private and for work!
Both for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
Fufu, what's with that. But, they could be used that way, I see...
You mean... Sending mails while calling me. Fufu~, it might be interesting.
高嶺
What would you think if I learned karate and aikido?
Eh, why those?
I saw it in the news last night. It was a junior high school girl, but I wanted to try it.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, do you have a gi...?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I will protect you!
What did you imagine?... Is it cute to wear a Keikogi?
Thank you. But... I also want to protect you. That said, it's okay, right?
高嶺
Hey, what would you do if we suddenly couldn't meet?
If I can't meet with you... ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Yes, I had such a dream last night... I was so sad...
I will do anything for you!
That can't happen
...Geez. If I was told that, it would make me feel stupid... Thank you...
Really?... You wont leave me and go away? Promise me.
高嶺
There are people who are good taking photos with a phone, right?
I'm here! I can make photos look good.
How can I be able to shoot like that? I want to know some tips.
Move like this, and pose
▲高嶺＊＊▲ you are already good!
...Something like this? How about this?... Geez, don't stay silent, say something will you? I'm embarrassed...
That's not helpful at all... Don't please me like that, I want to spoil you now...
高嶺
Hey, is there something you're hiding from me?
Hidding something!? Nothing like that!
To say it so quickly, isn't it suspicious? I won't be angry, can you be honest with me?
Hidden equals love, right?
I'll say I love you most!
Hmm, is that a reason? I'm kidding. But not so much, right? Otherwise, I'll be jealous.
...Why hide it? Even if you tell me every day, I...
Hey, can you say it again? ...This time, seriously... C'mon, hurry▼
高嶺
▲主人公＊▲.
Hmm? What?
Did I do something?
I'm sorry, it's nothing. I just wanted to call you▼
Yay, you understood▼ Well, I just wanted you to call my name.
高嶺
▲主人公＊▲. Have you ever wondered where your name comes from?
Umm, that's right...
I haven't bothered
I've heard from my parents
Is that so? Is it because you're a boy...?
Fufu, did you now? Is that a road everyone goes through once?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, can you call me, please.
高嶺
Huh? Umm... ▲主人公＊▲.
Hmm, I'm happy!
Fufu, if you like it, I'll do it as much as you want. ▲主人公＊▲.
▲主人公＊▲. Geez, what kind of game is that? Fufu!
